Anh - Anh
kora
['kɔ:rə]
■ noun a West African musical instrument shaped like a lute and played like a harp.
Origin
C18: a local word.

sentences.en: King begins with a K.
sentences.vi: Chữ King bắt đầu bằng chữ K.

sentences.vi: Ông ấy là Peter Smith, hay còn gọi là Louis Vuitton.

sentences.en: Mr. Baker, write it down B-A-K-E-R.

sentences.en: Is this OK? It's a K. C design.
